oracle.nosql.driver.values.JsonOptions

  • Packages that use JsonOptions 
    Package Description
    oracle.nosql.driver.ops
    Contains the input and response classes used for Oracle NoSQL Database Cloud operations.
    oracle.nosql.driver.values
    The classes in this package are used to represent and manipulate data in the Oracle NoSQL Database Cloud.
